@anchor{Variable clim:*help-gestures*}
@defvr {Variable} {clim:*help-gestures*}
@vindex clim:*help-gestures*
A list of the gesture names that cause @code{accept} and
@code{complete-input} to display a (possibly input context-sensitive)
help message, and for some presentation types a list of
possibilities as well. The exact global contents of this list is
unspecified, but must include the :help gesture name.
@end defvr
